Restricted Skins.name: Negev | dev_texture

Mil-Spec Skins.name: Nova | Windblown
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: It has been spray painted with a randomized pattern of a dandelion field.

Mil-Spec Skins.name: UMP-45 | Oscillator

Mil-Spec Skins.lore: Everyone has a breaking point; where's yours?

Mil-Spec Skins.name: CZ75-Auto | Circaetus
